cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset or code, please cite both the paper (once available) and this repository."
title: "ISO 15189 LLM Config Experiment: Dataset and Analysis Code"
abstract: >-
  Dataset, analysis code, and reproducibility materials for a study
  on LLM-assisted ISO 15189:2022 medical laboratory quality management
  system document generation. Includes 486 generated QMS documents
  (Claude Opus 4.6 and GPT-5.4) across 9 configuration groups and 15
  task types, 864 LLM-judge evaluations (Claude + GPT), and 10 expert
  blind-review ratings.
type: dataset
